==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: When the boat gets to either end of the bridge, it will automatically straighten itself out.
===Proverb===
{{cmn-proverb|s|pin=chuán dào qiáotóu zì rán zhí|pint=chuan2dao4qiao2tou2zi4ran2zhi2|tra=船到橋頭自然直|sim=船到桥头自然直|rs=舟05}}
# [[We'll cross that bridge when we come to it]].
